Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.41,0:02:22.41,ep,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追 憶 之 笛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.59,0:02:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 拉緊鋼索
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆 那邊太礙事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.27,0:02:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他搬走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.08,0:02:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不要隨便放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移動 到哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊 放那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 貨物都在那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.08,0:02:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 移動到那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.51,0:02:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.85,0:02:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以都叫你別用飛的了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 不要切斷鋼索
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.28,0:03:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你能自己想點辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何處理你的居住權 我們尚無定論
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你能暫時在這裡生活嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 在這種地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種地方太不方便了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡 就 行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 Chamber 附近 方便
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是賬單
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賬 單？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求貴官通過勞動補償對機庫造成的破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.53,0:03:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:03:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我們趕走海賊的可是雷德哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞機庫和那是兩回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 雷德剛剛來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不瞭解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.77,0:04:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們為他免除了逗留期間所消耗的水電費
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及將這龐然大物放在船上的裝載費
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是只有單方受益的霸王交易
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.91,0:04:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 這樣行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我具體內容
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這台人形機器人太礙事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移動 到哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想 去搬下一箱貨物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放到剛剛那個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber 移動到那邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.62,0:04:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說不要飛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.15,0:04:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這人形機器人不賴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙聽得懂你之外的人說的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的話他也會聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據軍紀 在允許範圍內
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可移交命令權
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可 以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆 我有個好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.66,0:05:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你的快遞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 在幹活在幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.49,0:05:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙搞啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓破廢鐵幹活 自己卻在一邊玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個大蠢材 果然還是應該把他丟進海裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家可能只是在休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法從貴官的行動中發現意義
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是集中精神的一種手段罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這麼熱的天 虧他們還能這麼好動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有紀律 他們的教官在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.62,0:06:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推測 兒童的訓練沒有教官參與
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要如何將他們培養成社會的一員呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請下達下一個命令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.44,0:06:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好詐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說說話嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.17,0:06:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛到天上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務執行出現障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請批准排除
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,批准
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.14,0:06:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意不要對他們造成傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 狀態怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待命 中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待命中？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.52,0:06:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.42,0:07:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？你在做什麼東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不知道還做啊 真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思議的材料呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希迪亞斯 指甲 這顆星球 上 沒有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.59,0:07:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的 話 就 送給 你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.56,0:07:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 我們邊走邊聊聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有好禮物可以送給弟弟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟 弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.41,0:07:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫貝貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的手很巧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何謂「弟弟」？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「弟弟」…就是兄弟的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比自己小的兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…家人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家 人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.62,0:07:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在舊社會中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:08:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基於雌雄配偶及血緣關係而構成的社會單位的名稱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來有過這樣的習俗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德沒有家人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.06,0:08:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低 效率 不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低效率…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得雷德住的地方很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝貝爾好像想問你關於宇宙的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙 的 事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他對天體啦 還有能飛向宇宙的交通工具
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.29,0:08:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他身體很虛弱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以無法自由活動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身 體 虛弱？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.11,0:08:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的胸部有點疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在銀河同盟中 體弱的人類將會被淘汰及處分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法參加戰鬥的人是沒有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用…怎麼能這樣 雷德你無所謂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不 懂 你 的提 問
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:08:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是否能從與那個人的對話中得到有意義的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.18,0:09:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情報？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 就去見見奧爾德姆醫生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧爾 德姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個醫生 不過大家都稱他為賢者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是加爾剛蒂亞裡知識最淵博的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.86,0:09:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 奧爾德姆醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生 艾米來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我帶了客人來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:10:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難道就是雷德嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說有事想問問醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我還有工作沒有做完
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.44,0:10:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德 一會兒我會來接你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下面等著我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方希望你提供情報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.46,0:10:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是聽到過傳言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是能理解語言的機械所發出的聲音嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.56,0:10:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這項技術已經失傳了 沒想到能親眼看到實物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 可以 提問 嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.97,0:10:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我能回答得上 你就儘管問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請坐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想知道什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想請教如何才能回到銀河同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:11:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 以我的知識無法回答你的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所見 大部分古老的智慧都已失傳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是行星穿梭技術
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們目前所保留的關於天空的知識
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它應該不是你所要找尋的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 幫不上你的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 也沒 辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.17,0:11:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 可以再 問 一個 問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.99,0:11:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 請說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想聽聽你對這個艦團組織的見解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.83,0:11:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂見解是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.19,0:11:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦團非常沒有效率
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令體系以及軍事訓練也不完善
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居民的行動也毫無秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法理解保護弱者的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.22,0:11:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外星來客是這樣看的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.85,0:12:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所指的效率似乎相當狹義啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不妨去見見貝貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是否能從與那個人的對話中得到有意義的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否有意義應該由你自己判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 醫生也不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝貝爾 我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,630)}歡迎回來 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.28,0:12:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人就是雷德哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:12:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真的是姐姐的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:12:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.99,0:13:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 我叫貝貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次 見面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是艾米的弟弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的話 請坐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德也說想見見貝貝爾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方希望你提供情報
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那個 難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 這就是Chamber的通信機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.81,0:13:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 真的會說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是Chamber先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.39,0:13:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本機是用於支援駕駛員的人工智能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好酷 地球的語言也能理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米 在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.95,0:13:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們人手不夠了 你快來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 帥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我得去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.96,0:13:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得現在氣氛正好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.11,0:14:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼氣氛正好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.06,0:14:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說不是你想的那樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 貝貝爾 雷德就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太急了 小心摔倒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.17,0:14:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.81,0:14:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.79,0:14:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 姐姐總是匆匆忙忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德哥哥 你真的是從宇宙來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.76,0:14:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很在意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙的生活是什麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.77,0:14:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀河同盟的主要任務是與希迪亞斯進行戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希迪亞斯是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.13,0:14:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威脅人類生存的異種生物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們一直在戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.35,0:14:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從銀河同盟創立至今 戰鬥從未停止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.34,0:14:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這裡的生活完全不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會累嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不堪消耗者唯有死亡一途
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:14:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 真的很艱辛呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.23,0:15:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你習慣這裡的生活了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法理解加爾剛蒂亞的組織構造
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組織？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請解釋低效及無意義經營的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦團不是組織啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是大家聚在一起罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時而吵架 時而互幫互助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以這樣的方式活下去罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.11,0:15:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問意義何在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都能安心地活著不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對此回答感到不解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的行動目的應該是討伐敵人希迪亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則人類無法獲得穩定的發展
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.81,0:15:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在銀河同盟中 你這樣的人類會立刻被淘汰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淘汰…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.93,0:16:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果將希迪亞斯全部都消滅的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀河同盟會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德哥哥你會怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.48,0:16:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在收到下一道命令之前待命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.88,0:16:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 如果沒有下一道命令呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有繼續待命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就和我們一樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.69,0:16:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樣 嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.81,0:16:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為待命不就是指一直活下去的意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你的人形機器人被喬給搶走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.16,0:16:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得當了次英雄 現在卻不成樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道自己的行動是否有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.19,0:17:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是幫我們趕走海賊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.82,0:17:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我只是在監視Chamber而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.37,0:17:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是還沒適應
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法判斷我應該採取什麼行動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.23,0:17:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該採取的行動啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先放棄你那軍人思維怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放 棄？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 更加自由地…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雨！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.28,0:17:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集雨水！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼 發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是氣象現象 沒有毒性
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.06,0:17:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生緊急事態了 用你的人形機器人來收集雨水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.98,0:17:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淡水可是很珍貴的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.90,0:17:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要 怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊有帆布 把它展開來收集雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 就這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.49,0:18:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴官的腦波產生了變化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在意友軍的戰況
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在目前狀況下 貴官的思考毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現帥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他果然好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 總覺得他好可憐…一個人流落到陌生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.39,0:18:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個帥哥沒事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.95,0:18:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你很擔心他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.93,0:19:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.89,0:19:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你濕透了呢 會感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.35,0:19:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來我家把身體擦乾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.14,0:19:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的驟雨很大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.66,0:19:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次觀測到集中降雨現象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.27,0:19:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙中也會下雨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,0:19:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有海嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.88,0:19:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我這樣的病人也…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.64,0:19:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我並不認為自己是不被需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢 還有姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.92,0:19:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾 米？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德哥哥也是一直被別人所需要才能活到現在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:20:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有對戰鬥有益的人才需要存活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.44,0:20:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 反向思考一下 對雷德哥哥來說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有你覺得需要的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.25,0:20:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和姐姐 彼此都需要對方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.76,0:20:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是 我需要我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我活著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.97,0:20:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對同盟而言 無意義者沒有生存的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.88,0:20:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 這對你來說是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽姐姐說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.05,0:20:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道這是什麼 卻在製作著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一定是笛子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.36,0:20:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥中完全不需要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笛 子？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.64,0:20:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 它可以發出聲音哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.19,0:21:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷德哥哥？你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.39,0:21:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說錯什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是 我也不 知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.78,0:21:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是想起什麼悲傷的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.56,0:21:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 這樣 嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.53,0:21:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你 把它 還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.23,0:21:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶泡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.99,0:21:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是紗雅推薦的 很好喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chamber 還是無法定位坐標嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.11,0:21:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀測情報不足 仍需要時間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.62,0:21:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.12,0:22:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來還需要進一步瞭解這個星球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.44,0:22:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有必要 貴官早晚將與主力部隊會合
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.93,0:22:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道的
